      "title": "Deadline to apply for A/L extended",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The deadline for accepting applications for the 2022 G.C.E Advanced Level Examination has been extended to the 26th of August.",
        "This was announced by the Commissioner General of Examination L. M. D. Dharmasena.",
        "The extension is mainly for the candidates who wish to sit for the examination after the results of the 2021 G. C. E. Advanced Level Examination is released."
      ],
